15:49.580 --> 15:53.480
The head of the Simons Foundation, a guy named Dr. David Spurgle,

15:53.900 --> 15:57.680
he was tapped to be the chair of the NASA UAP working group.

15:57.680 --> 16:02.840
Yeah. A working group that sort of says, you know, nothing to see here.

16:02.960 --> 16:06.760
Like, we'll keep an open mind, but there's probably nothing here, which I find interesting.

16:07.120 --> 16:09.060
Yeah. I mean, I don't know. I have no smoking gun.

16:09.120 --> 16:11.660
